ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Justice how many (a) male and (b) female clergy have been appointed by his Department in each of the last five years.

reply.p: The figures requested are as follows:
In the same period, the Lord Chancellor has also appointed one female Canon Residentiary in 2006, and four male Canon Residentiaries, one in each of 2006, 2007 and 2008.
